## Test Files

**Match class name with `_test` suffix:**

```ruby
# Model tests
# File: test/models/user_test.rb
class UserTest < ActiveSupport::TestCase
end

# File: test/models/blog_post_test.rb
class BlogPostTest < ActiveSupport::TestCase
end

# Controller tests
# File: test/controllers/articles_controller_test.rb
class ArticlesControllerTest < ActionDispatch::IntegrationTest
end

# System tests
# File: test/system/articles_test.rb
class ArticlesTest < ApplicationSystemTestCase
end

# Job tests
# File: test/jobs/article_notification_job_test.rb
class ArticleNotificationJobTest < ActiveSupport::TestCase
end
```

